---
// Hero component — Central de Vistos
---

<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sora:wght@400;600;800&family=Inter:wght@400;500&display=swap');

  /* ── FLOW SECTION ── */
  .flow-section {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 60px 0 48px;
  }

  .flow-title {
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: #0A1628;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .flow-subtitle {
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 3vw, 1.75rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #0A1628;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .flow-subtitle em {
    font-style: normal;
    color: #1A56DB;
  }

  /* steps grid */
  .steps-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
    gap: 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* connector line between steps */
  .steps-grid::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 80px; /* center of the image */
    left: calc(10% + 16px);
    right: calc(10% + 16px);
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1A56DB 0%, #60A5FA 100%);
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0 10px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  /* step image wrapper */
  .step-img-wrap {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    border-radius: 14px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    position: relative;
    border: 3px solid #fff;
    outline: 2px solid #E2E8F0;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }
  .step-img-wrap:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(26,86,219,0.18);
    outline-color: #1A56DB;
  }

  /* step number badge */
  .step-num {
    position: absolute;
    top: 10px;
    left: 10px;
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    background: #1A56DB;
    color: #fff;
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    z-index: 2;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
  }

  .step-img-wrap img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .step-label {
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0A1628;
    line-height: 1.35;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .step-desc {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.90rem;
    color: #64748B;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* arrow between steps (hidden on mobile) */
  .step-arrow {
    position: absolute;
    right: -10px;
    top: 40px;
    color: #1A56DB;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  /* last step highlight */
  .step:last-child .step-img-wrap {
    outline-color: #FFD600;
  }
  .step:last-child .step-num {
    background: #FFD600;
    color: #0A1628;
  }

  /* footer note */
  .flow-footer {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #94A3B8;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 32px;
  }
  .flow-footer strong {
    color: #1A56DB;
  }

  /* responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .steps-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .steps-grid::before { display: none; }
    .step-arrow { display: none; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .steps-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>


<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════
     COMO FUNCIONA  (flow section)
════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="flow-section">
  <div class="container px-4 mx-auto">





    <!-- ── section heading ── -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">

      <!-- eyebrow -->
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="block h-px w-8" style="background:#1A56DB;"></span>
        <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase" style="color:#1A56DB; font-family:'Sora',sans-serif;">Nossa metodologia</span>
        <span class="block h-px w-8" style="background:#1A56DB;"></span>
      </div>

      <!-- title -->
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-3" style="font-family:'Sora',sans-serif; color:#0A1628; letter-spacing:-0.03em;">
        Como Funciona?
      </h2>

      <!-- subtitle -->
      <p class="text-base text-slate-500 max-w-lg mx-auto" style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;">
        Simples, transparente e sem surpresas — do primeiro contato ao visto carimbado no seu passaporte.
      </p>

    </div>





    <div class="steps-grid">

      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-img-wrap">
          <span class="step-num">1</span>
          <img src="assets/images/hero/freepik__a-professional-customer-support-specialist-wearing__1452.png" alt="Fale com um especialista" loading="lazy"/>
        </div>
        <p class="step-label">Fale com um especialista</p>
        <p class="step-desc">Nossa equipe orienta você passo a passo e coleta todas as informações.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-img-wrap">
          <span class="step-num">2</span>
          <img src="assets/images/hero/freepik__a-photorealistic-logistics-scene-showing-an-intern__1453.png" alt="Envio seguro de documentos" loading="lazy"/>
        </div>
        <p class="step-label">Envio seguro de documentos</p>
        <p class="step-desc">Programamos a coleta do passaporte via <strong>Sedex</strong> com rastreamento.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-img-wrap">
          <span class="step-num">3</span>
          <img src="assets/images/hero/freepik__a-photorealistic-office-scene-showing-a-profession__1454.png" alt="Equipe especializada acompanha" loading="lazy"/>
        </div>
        <p class="step-label">Equipe especializada acompanha</p>
        <p class="step-desc">Seu passaporte é recebido próximo aos consulados em São Paulo.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 4 -->
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-img-wrap">
          <span class="step-num">4</span>
          <img src="assets/images/hero/freepik__a-photorealistic-closeup-of-a-person-holding-a-mod__1455.png" alt="Acompanhamento em tempo real" loading="lazy"/>
        </div>
        <p class="step-label">Acompanhamento em tempo real</p>
        <p class="step-desc">Você recebe atualizações e suporte sempre que precisar.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 5 — highlight -->
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-img-wrap">
          <span class="step-num">5</span>
          <img src="assets/images/hero/freepik__the-attached-drawing-is-provided-only-as-a-visual-__1456.png" alt="Passaporte com visto pronto" loading="lazy"/>
        </div>
        <p class="step-label">Seu passaporte retorna com o visto pronto 🎉</p>
        <p class="step-desc">Com segurança e acompanhamento personalizado do início ao fim.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>